    "n_faq_content_BEUB9R": {
      "type": "n_faq-content",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_aTR4Yi": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What is the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear?",
            "text": "<p>Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is a face mask that puts professional LED therapy in your hands so you can operate easily, all by yourself, in the comfort of your own home!</p><p>It comes with a compatible iOS/Android app that allows you to fully customize, track and plan your treatments.</p>",
            "section_id": "Technology"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_a4miCD": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How does Qure’s Light Therapy technology work?",
            "text": "<p>Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear uses clinical-grade technology to deliver safe, concentrated wavelengths of light directly to the underlying layers of your skin. </p><p>The optimal wavelengths of light are absorbed by your skin cells and kick start the production of collagen, elastin, and fibroblasts. </p><p>In turn, this stimulates mechanisms within the skin that solve skin problems and concerns from the inside out.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_Pj7A8R": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How many LEDs does the Q-Rejuvalight Pro have and what wavelengths?",
            "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro has a total of 5 clinically-proven wavelengths of lights:</p><ul><li>Infrared light (880 nm): Increases circulation, protects existing collagen and enhances product absorption.</li><li>Deep Red (660 nm): Accelerates skin healing to fade and prevent scarring. Builds collagen to help reduce wrinkles.</li><li>Red (630 nm): Stimulates collagen and elastin production, firms and plumps skin, repairs skin cells and promotes hydration to help reduce inflammation, redness and rosacea.</li><li>Amber (605 nm): Reduces appearance of dark spots. Soothes skin and calms swelling and inflammation.</li><li>Blue (415 nm): Anti-bacterial, eliminates and prevents acne breakouts. Soothes and calms skin.</li></ul><p>There are three treatment modes:</p><ul><li>The Pro-Aging Treatment</li><li>The Anti-Breakout Treatment</li><li>Custom zone selection on five facial areas via the Qure app.</li></ul>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_g4mtBM": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Does the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear use infrared light as well?",
            "text": "<p>Yes! The Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear uses red, infrared, amber, and deep red lights for the Pro-Aging treatment.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PienAH": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What does the Skin Rejuvenating mode treat?",
            "text": "<p>The Skin Rejuvenating Treatment combines red, deep red, infrared and amber wavelengths which is why the LED lights appear to be an orange color. This combination stimulates collagen, help reduce redness, fine lines, dark spots while encouraging the skin to heal and rejuvenate itself, for visibly smoother, firmer, younger-looking skin. </p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_AXrMDh": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What does the Skin Clearing mode treat?",
            "text": "<p>The Skin Clearing Treatment combines red and blue wavelengths to destroy the bacteria that causes acne, regulate oil production, reduce redness and other symptoms when a flare-up occurs for clearer skin.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_wjtMGF": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Can I customize my Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear treatment routine?",
            "text": "<p>Yes! While each Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear comes with a recommended pre-programmed treatment routine, you can personalize your treatments and experience by creating your own treatment routine via the Qure Skincare app. </p><p>You can choose your preferred treatment mode (Pro-Aging or Anti-Breakout) on 5 different facial areas.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_GN3gtL": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Is the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear safe to use?",
            "text": "<p>Yes! Light therapy has been studied and tested across hundreds of peer-reviewed clinical trials, with overwhelmingly positive results for skin health. </p><p>The treatment is pain free, non-invasive, requires no surgery and is a completely safe and effective treatment for all skin types.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_pEnpkb": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Should I protect and close my eyes during treatment?",
            "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro has been tested and cleared for eye safety. It has successfully passed the IEC62471 evaluation for eye safety test, which is used to determine whether a device's light output is safe for the eyes or not.Regardless, we recommend closing your eyes and wearing protective eyewear duringtreatment.The light can be bright when powered on and some users may experience sensitivity, even when closing their eyes.</p><p>As part of our unwavering commitment to your safety we decided to take the initiative to include certified light blocking protective eyewear with our Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED mask.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_agNxHf": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Does my Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear work without the app?",
            "text": "<p>You can manually use your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear without using the app. However if you’re wanting to customize your treatment on different areas on your face, then this will need to be done via the Qure Skincare app.</p><p>To choose/change a full treatment without using the app, follow the instructions below:</p><ul><li>Power on the device by holding the Q button on forehead until the led indicator light is on</li><li>Press the button once for Pro-Aging Treatment</li><li>Press it again for Anti-Breakout Treatment</li><li>Switch off the device by holding down the Q button until the indicator light turns off</li></ul>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_B4BF94": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Where can I fit in the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear in my daily skin care routine?",
            "text": "<p>You may easily fit in a 3-minute treatment right after you wash and dry your face. The only important thing to remember is that your face should be clean before the treatment. Once the treatment is done, you may proceed in applying serums and creams to your skin as desired!</p>",
            "section_id": "Results"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_rchTtz": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How often can I use my Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear?",
            "text": "<p>One of the best things about the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is that you only need to use it once per day. That's how effective the treatment is! </p><p>For best results, we recommend that you do your 3 minute treatment daily. You may also do one full Pro-Aging treatment and one full Anti-Breakout treatment per day.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_6eXwmb": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How long will it take before I start seeing results?",
            "text": "<p>Depending on what skin concern you’re wanting to treat.</p><p>With daily use, users will typically notice a reduction in acne breakouts after just 2 weeks!</p><p>While users typically see visible improvement of wrinkles, fine lines and signs of aging, as well as improved skin tone and smoothness after 8-12 weeks.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_UQdzLj": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Can I use the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear with retinol and microneedling routine?",
            "text": "<p>You can use the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear within days of microneedling since light therapy can speed up recovery time! Retinol is a treatment that helps slough skin away so you can use light therapy after this as well.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_fKVwF6": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How do I start my first treatment?",
            "text": "<p>Activate your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear via the Qure Skincare app, or follow the How To Use guide, which can be found inside the box.</p><p>After cleansing your face, place our Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear comfortably over the face, securing strap around head. Press and hold the Q power button on forehead for 3 seconds to turn on our Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear, select treatment mode on the app (Pro-Aging or Anti-Breakout) and start your treatment!</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_xVbCJY": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How do I charge my Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear?",
            "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro is USB-rechargeable. A two and a half hour charge can deliver up to 10 treatments. Plug into an USB power adaptor,input should be 5V/1A, the voltage should no more than 5V.</p><p>Plug the USB-C power/charging cord into the port connector of your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear, then plug it into a universal USB power adapter. Device is fully charged when the red power indicator light next to the charging port is turned off.</p>",
            "section_id": "Charging Q-Rejuvalight Pro"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_jwxEAE": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Can the Q Rejuvalight Pro Facewear be used while charging?",
            "text": "<p>No, you cannot turn on the device while charging for safety reasons.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_HJ84eW": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What does it mean when my Q-Rejuvalight Pro is continuously blinking?",
            "text": "<p>A blinking light around device indicates that your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is low in battery and needs to be charged.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_3y4nPr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What’s included in the box?",
            "text": "<p>Inside the box, you'll find:</p><ul><li>Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Face Mask</li><li>Adjustable head strap for a secure, comfortable fit</li><li>USB-C charging cable</li><li>Portable luxury storage pouch</li><li>Clear setup instructions and user manual</li></ul>",
            "section_id": "Storing Q-Rejuvalight Pro"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_cQM6Bi": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How do I properly store my Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear?",
            "text": "<p>We recommend to keep your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear in a dry environment and always keeping your Q-Rejuvalight Pro in the storage bag when not using it. </p><p>Usually, the bathroom is not the best place for keeping your Qure device due to the heightened moisture in a bathroom.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_N3q6zf": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "What is the best way to clean the Q-Rejuvalight Pro after use?",
            "text": "<p>Wipe the inside with a damp cloth to remove any residue from skin oils after each use. Make sure the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is unplugged and turned off. Then use a damp, soft, or microfiber cloth to clean the facial area. Repeat until the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is clean and then dry with a clean dry cloth.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_7wwtna": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "How do I prevent the inner mask silicone from discoloration?",
            "text": "<p>Make sure to clean your face thoroughly before use! Residue from make ups or other creams/serums can cause discoloration.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_dL9jdc": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": true,
            "heading": "How do I secure the strap to my Q-Rejuvalight Pro?",
            "text": "",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_qKKEke": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Is the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear BPA free?",
            "text": "<p>We always aim to provide excellent products to our customers to make them beautiful and healthy! Therefore, the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear is BPA free.</p>",
            "section_id": "Safety"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_dJxNtJ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Is it safe to use LED light therapy while pregnant or breastfeeding?",
            "text": "<p>For those pregnant or breastfeeding, we recommend checking with your doctor before starting Red Light therapy treatments.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_eez4Xg": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Does the Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear come with a warranty?",
            "text": "<p>Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear comes with one (1) year warranty covering any manufacturer related problems resulting from everyday use of the product. However, this device is designed to last years! </p><p>For more information on warranty, please visit <a href=\"#\">Our Warranty Policy</a></p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_GdiJfU": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Is the Q-Rejuvalight Pro FDA-cleared?",
            "text": "<p>Yes! Our Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED mask is the world’s first customizable, FDA-cleared at-home LED mask that's proven to be an effective and safe treatment for acne and aging skin concerns.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        }
      },
