    "n_faq_content_EgyaBi": {
      "type": "n_faq-content",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_mVNEnW": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear Warranty",
            "text": "<p>This 1-year limited warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship in your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear when purchased directly from Qure Skincare. Your 1-year limited warranty is valid for you alone, the original purchaser, and cannot be transferred.</p><p>If the product was a gift then please obtain a copy of the original receipt or have the original purchaser process the warranty claim on your behalf. This warranty does not cover: damage, defects, failure caused by abuse or misuse, improper care, impact or insertion of foreign objects, use with a voltage connector, or loss of device.</p><p>The limited warranty begins from the date of delivery and expires after one year. The warranty period is not extended if your device is replaced by Qure during the warranty period.</p><p><strong>To make a warranty claim:</strong><br /> If you discover a defect in your Q-Rejuvalight Pro Facewear that is covered by the warranty, before the warranty period expires, contact Qure customer support for assistance via email or live chat.</p><p>If we confirm a defect covered by this limited warranty, Qure will decide whether to replace your device. If we find that your device is not defective, we will notify you and return the device to you. All limited warranty services must be authorized and performed by Qure.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QkCPUR": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "secure_strap": false,
            "heading": "Q-Renew LLLT Helmet Warranty",
            "text": "<p>The 24-month limited warranty covers defects in materials and workmanship in your Q-Renew LLLT Helmet when purchased directly from Qure Skincare. Your 1-year limited warranty is valid for you alone, the original purchaser, and cannot be transferred.</p><p>If the product was a gift then please obtain a copy of the original receipt or have the original purchaser process the warranty claim on your behalf. This warranty does not cover: damage, defects, failure caused by abuse or misuse, improper care, impact or insertion of foreign objects, use with a voltage connector, or loss of device.</p><p>The limited warranty begins from the date of purchase and expires after 24 months. The warranty period is not extended if your device is replaced by Qure during the warranty period.</p><p><strong>To make a warranty claim:</strong><br /> If you discover a defect in your Q-Renew LLLT Helmet that is covered by the warranty, before the warranty period expires, contact Qure customer support for assistance via email or live chat. </p><p>Provide your full name, proof of purchase, device serial number, a detailed description of the issues, and photos or videos if available. If a defect is confirmed, Qure Skincare will replace the device. Non-defective devices will be returned to you.</p>",
            "section_id": ""
          }
        }
      },
